 Lazygit

 Panels
  1                        status
  2                        files
  3                        branches
  4                        commits
  5                        stash

 Actions
  Space                    stage/unstage file
  a                        stage all
  c                        commit
  p                        push
  P                        pull
  Enter                    view diff
  d                        discard changes

 Navigation
  j/k                      up/down
  h/l                      switch panels
  /                        search
  ?                        full keybind list
  q                        quit
